Hello!
Happy Monday! I see there are a few new faces here so I thought i’d re- introduce myself.
My name is Donia.
I am a mom of 3. I lived in Rome Italy and moved to the US 9 years ago.
I have always loved fashion, i grow into DIY-ing since my move ( i never saw the good in anything old) but now i see the gold beneath the wood😍 and getting really good at it. 
I started this page to help challenge myself.  Personally i can be shy around people but this platform has helped me build more confidence in myself and along the way i have made wonderful friends like all of you. I love to try new things and Today i am grateful to have your support and love. 
Hopefully I inspire someone out there. 💓
.
My something new is photography. I just tried taking pictures of myself instead of the kids. What do you think?
.
